    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay, so if i went with the robust regression like you said, would that actually stabilize the model enough? i'm just worried about these specific points that are totally messing up the distribution. they feel almost \"unpredictable\" or like they're just intentionally breaking the pattern of the rest of the data.",
